# Cloudflare Pages — _redirects
#
# Old gated path was /preview/*. The site has been promoted to root, with
# the gate now scoped to / by functions/_middleware.js. Anyone hitting an
# old /preview/* bookmark is moved to the equivalent root path with a
# permanent (301) redirect so search engines and browsers update.
#
# Match order: most specific first. The :splat placeholder captures
# everything matched by `*`.

/preview      /        301
/preview/     /        301
/preview/*    /:splat  301
